INSERT INTO `wp_photo_postmeta` VALUES (1916, 528, 'text', '"Owen and Charis have produced fantastic results for Pear Tree over the past year. They have a rare talent that enables them to capture the moment and fulfil any brief. They are incredibly easy to work and highly efficient. I would promote them to any organisation needing high quality photography." Tim Partridge');
INSERT INTO `wp_photo_postmeta` VALUES (1917, 529, 'text', 'Please contact us and give us more information about your needs. We will devise a quote based on your personal shoot tailored to you.');
INSERT INTO `wp_photo_postmeta` VALUES (1918, 530, 'text', '"Its so hard to find natural-looking stock images to suit our needs and target audience. We love o&c photography. The images are fresh, unique, and just what we want! Thank you." Looking at life');
INSERT INTO `wp_photo_postmeta` VALUES (1919, 533, 'text', 'Our approach to portrait photography is a relaxed one that provides an easy environment for the subject to be themselves in.  We capture personality as well as images, and offer a range of products including prints, mounted photographs, canvas and photobooks.\r\n\r\nCapturing a special occasion with a photoshoot will ensure the memories remain forever.  So if youre expecting a baby or have just reached your 100th birthday - and for everything in between, you can mark it with a portrait.');
INSERT INTO `wp_photo_postmeta` VALUES (1920, 534, 'text', '175 (including 50 of print credit)');
INSERT INTO `wp_photo_postmeta` VALUES (1921, 535, 'text', '"Owen & Charis were amazing on our photo shoot. It was so relaxed & we had lots of fun, they worked so hard yet made it look effortless.  They really put us as ease and getting the natural shots the did is a real art. o&c had lots of great ideas and embraced ours.  Theyre a top professional team.  We were blown away when we saw the photos...we love them so much. The hardest bit for us in all of this is choosing which prints to put up as they are all stunning! We will always treasure them. We would highly recommend this talented duo who you can trust to capture your special memories perfectly."\r\nSteve and Hannah');
