INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (229, 1, '2010-04-13 10:43:00', '2010-04-13 10:43:00', 'What an honour to capture the very precious time of pregnancy. With only 6 weeks to go, Charlotte has a beautiful and very neat baby bump. Phil and Charlotte were keen to get out to the sea for some photos as they live in Bournemouth and are regular visitors to the sea for a spot of wind surfing and kite surfing. We dont have any photos of these particular activities although Owen and Phil did partake in some in between our photo shoots! With the stunning carpet of celandines in our garden and the beautiful Pembrokeshire sun pouring down we were so chuffed with the perfect day we had. Phil and Charlotte do not have a name for their baby "boy" yet, but we are hoping that they can be persuaded in to calling him "Elvis"! We are very excited for you both and look forward to meeting "Baby Elvis!" in a couple of months. God bless you and thank you for allowing us to capture images of you both at this special time in your lives x<br><br>For more photos please check out our work at <a href="http://www.oacphotography.com/">www.oacphotography.com</a> and please contact us if you too would like a maternity shoot<br><br><a href="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4020/4517653852_9b83a07d3a_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4020/4517653852_9b83a07d3a_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4008/4517653998_8ef234642e_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4008/4517653998_8ef234642e_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4023/4517657532_596379327c_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4023/4517657532_596379327c_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4043/4517657400_72734bd292_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4043/4517657400_72734bd292_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2683/4517024379_bf296ecf6a