INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (230, 1, '2010-04-03 15:40:00', '2010-04-03 15:40:00', 'You can never guarantee good weather in Spring and West Wales, but the weather for this wedding was nothing but perfect. Sam and Katie (Knott) married at Broad Haven Baptist Church in Pembrokeshire, with their reception at <a href="http://www.cuffernmanor.co.uk/">Cuffern Manor</a>. Being a Welsh wedding there were plenty of stunning daffodils and spring flowers (thanks to Katies mum, who grew most of them in her garden) adorning the church, reception and displayed in the stunning bouquets. Katie wore amazing green shoes, which matched the stunning bridesmaids. Sam with his dreads oozed coolness with his posse of grooms men (some of the most helpful we have ever worked with...thanks so much guys!)You cant really do a coastal wedding without visiting the beach. We drove down to Nolton Haven for the beach shots and were lucky enough to have some stunning early evening light and an empty beach. Both Sam and Katie are both beach lovers, spending many a day surfing and having fun in the sea, so this location was perfect to capture this side of their relationship.Mr and Mrs Knott we wish you so much happiness in your new life. Thanks for a truly awesome day x <br><br>Please check out <a href="http://www.oacphotography.com/index.html">www.oacphotography.com</a> for more of our work.<br><br><a href="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4071/4486426651_ee78b84aef_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4071/4486426651_ee78b84aef_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2789/4486426957_44bc521bc6_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2789/4486426957_44bc521bc6_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4044/4487078202_33ddc23cee_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4044/4487078202_33ddc23cee_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4047/4486427719_4d7fe80fe0_o