INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (293, 1, '2010-07-11 20:37:00', '2010-07-11 20:37:00', '<a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDo2a8VJfjI/AAAAAAAAACk/zDYMtlpMkF8/s1600/Phil+and+Charlotte-077.jpg"><img src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDo2a8VJfjI/AAAAAAAAACk/zDYMtlpMkF8/s400/Phil+and+Charlotte-077.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br>While most of the world is watching the World Cup Finale, including Owen, I thought I would put up a cheeky sneak peek from a very special wedding in Leamington Spa last weekend. More to come once the couple in question return from their honey-mooning :D<br><br><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDo2TupThaI/AAAAAAAAACc/Zjm74hSNSQY/s1600/DSC_1492.jpg"><img src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDo2TupThaI/AAAAAAAAACc/Zjm74hSNSQY/s400/DSC_1492.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a>', 'Sneak Peek - Leamington Spa wedding', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sneak-peek-leamington-spa-wedding', '', '', '2010-07-11 20:37:00', '2010-07-11 20:37:00', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.84/oc/?p=209', 0, 'post', '', 1);
INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (294, 1, '2010-07-06 13:36:00', '2010-07-06 13:36:00', 'We are so chuffed to have one of our weddings featured in the July/August issue <a href="http://www.yoursouthwaleswedding.co.uk/">"Your SOUTH WALES Wedding"</a> magazine. We loved capturing the wedding day of Sam and Katie back in May. They are truly awesome people with such a special love for each other. Pembrokeshire is such a beautiful county and having the opportunity to capture this newly wed couple on the beach at Nolton Haven was such fun. We totally understand why they love the sea and Pembrokeshire. Its for these reasons that we moved here too!<br>It is so exciting to see our work in print and in the next few months we are to be featured in some other magazines, but you will have to wait a bit longer for those! <br>Thank you so much Sam and Katie for your lovely feature and for being such a fab pair to photograph and to spend the day with on your wedding day and thank you Danielle for contacting us about featuring our work x o&c<br><br><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDMx-f8PlvI/AAAAAAAAACE/emjgboCC_QU/s1600/LexmarkAIOScan1.jpg"><img src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDMx-f8PlvI/AAAAAAAAACE/emjgboCC_QU/s400/LexmarkAIOScan1.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDMx40hKyvI/AAAAAAAAAB8/lC58XhZH7sE/s1600/LexmarkAIOScan2.jpg"><img src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDMx40hKyvI/AAAAAAAAAB8/lC58XhZH7sE/s400/LexmarkAIOScan2.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDMxzKLJtbI/AAAAAAAAAB0/SJACdktDezg/s1600/LexmarkAIOScan3.jpg"><img src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDMxzKLJtbI/AAAAAAAAAB0/SJACdktDezg/s400/LexmarkAIOScan3.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDMxrsnFn2I/AAAAAAAAABs/qVzYf9zSrVU/s1600/LexmarkAIOScan4.jpg"><img src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDMxrsnFn2I/AAAAAAAAABs/qVzYf9zSrVU/s400/LexmarkAIOScan4.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br>We even made it to the Editors favourites too with this image of Katie preparing the leave for the church. Yay! We love this image too :D<br><br><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDMxhHu7SMI/AAAAAAAAABk/f5iA-K8Stx4/s1600/LexmarkAIOScan5.jpg"><img src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_q0_lRF4hcJ4/TDMxhHu7SMI/AAAAAAAAABk/f5iA-K8Stx4/s400/LexmarkAIOScan5.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br>If you are enjoying what you see on this blog please feel free to check out our website here at <a href="http://www.oacphotography.com/wedding.html">www.oacphotography.com </a>', 'Your SOUTH WALES Wedding - Real Wedding Feature', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'your-south-wales-wedding-real-wedding-feature', '', '', '2010-07-06 13:36:00', '2010-07-06 13:36:00', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.84/oc/?p=210', 0, 'post', '', 3);
INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (295, 1, '2010-06-28 15:52:00', '2010-06-28 15:52:00', 'This week we have had our work featured on two of the most awesome UK wedding blogs. <br>We became sponsors for the very lovely <a href="http://www.lovemydress.net/">Love My Dress blog</a> earlier this month and were featured this week with the stunning wedding of Damian and Katie in May - <a href="http://www.lovemydress.net/blog/2010/06/vw-camper-van-wedding.html">"A VW ''LoveDub'' Campervan Style Wedding"</a>. Annabel has featured us a couple of times now. We feel so honoured as we love what she does and it means so much to be featured alongside some truly amazing photographers and others in the industry. Have a little peek at the recent o&c Photography features from Love My Dress  - <a href="http://www.lovemydress.net/blog/2010/05/vintage-wedding-in-wales.html">"A Vintage Weddding in Wales"</a>, <a href="http://www.lovemydress.net/blog/2010/05/caravan-of-lola-love.html">"Caravan of Lola Love"</a>, <a href="http://www.lovemydress.net/blog/2010/06/oac-photography.html">"o&c Photography - New Sponsors"</a>, <a href="http://www.lovemydress.net/blog/2010/06/a-vintage-engagement-shoot-.html">"A Vintage Engagement Shoot - Sun, Sea & Suitcases"</a>...hope you enjoy! Thanks Annabel for yet again making us feel so loved by Love My Dress :D <br><br> As if all that bloggage love was not enough...Today we have had our work featured on the uber-cool <a href="http://www.rocknrollbride.com/">Rock''nRoll Bride Blog</a> alongside a selection of truly awesome photographers from the recent <a href="http://www.rocknrollbride.com/2010/06/the-photography-parlour-and-the-g2g-shoot-out/">Photography Parlour G2G</a>. Pink-haired Kat is the groovesome wedding blogger for Rock''n Roll Bride. Her blog is full of amazing features including rock and roll weddings, engagement shoots and wedding related articles. We are so chuffed to have been chosen for this feauture and love how Kat has styled her blog. Thanks Kat, its such an honour and we hope we get the chance to work with you again, real soon x<br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1359/4727081119_4e673c3de1_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1359/4727081119_4e673c3de1_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a>', 'Love My Dress and Rock ''n Roll Bride features! Oh Yes!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'love-my-dress-and-rock-n-roll-bride-features-oh-yes', '', '', '2010-06-28 15:52:00', '2010-06-28 15:52:00', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.84/oc/?p=211', 0, 'post', '', 3);
INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (296, 1, '2010-06-28 14:41:00', '2010-06-28 14:41:00', 'So, when we were contacted by Laura asking if we could capture her family as a Fathers Day present for her husband Paul, I was really excited. Before going full time with Photography, I (Charis) was a full-time teacher. Laura and Pauls eldest daughter was in my class and I had also taught their son. It was so exciting to see them again, they truly are a gorgeous family. I had really hoped for good weather and had an idea in my head of what I envisaged from the shoot. After chatting to Laura I realised that our ideas were the same! Good start! I had an idea of where we should go, but as we no longer live in Oxford, it was a chance of luck that the field I was hoping to go to would be full of flowers. As we drove around the corner I was so chuffed! Whoopeee!!! buttercups galore! It was so stunning and a true find. <br>Since I last saw Laura and Paul and their family they have a new baby son, so they really wanted photos to capture their whole family, with focus on the children. As usual I had a few props, which ended up being very useful as we did have a couple of moans and groans from the children, but they really worked well with the camera and made the job easy and very much fun!<br>Thank you so much guys for letting us capture your gorgeous family and thank you for being so up for playing in the beautiful buttercups! Big love from us x o&c<br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1199/4727735775_b0cc160dde_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1199/4727735775_b0cc160dde_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1398/4728382254_fb528becd7_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1398/4728382254_fb528becd7_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1152/4728383922_6e721f1e4a_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1152/4728383922_6e721f1e4a_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br>