INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (297, 1, '2010-06-25 07:16:00', '2010-06-25 07:16:00', '<a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1174/4732592232_6b59075489_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1174/4732592232_6b59075489_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br>We received two Thank You card in the post this week. They have really made our day and each card has said the kindest things. Its funny how words can mean so much. They are so easy to say, but also so easy not to say.<br>We are not writing this in expectation of thanks from anyone, but just as a celebration of two little words "Thank You".<br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1086/4731949467_cd82b9b878_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1086/4731949467_cd82b9b878_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1196/4731948445_48130bb1fd_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1196/4731948445_48130bb1fd_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1359/4732592578_8727ce1fa3_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1359/4732592578_8727ce1fa3_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br>Stationary designed by <a href="http://oacphotography.blogspot.com/random.panda@live.co.uk">Sarah Joy</a>.<br><br>Also, we have been blown away by the stunning designs of invites that have been coming our way recently. Design is such a personal thing and when preparing a wedding, design can set the style of your whole day. Here are some truly wonderful examples of just some of the invites we have recently received for weddings. When we got married we made our own invites using a photograph of the beach where we got engaged.<br>These examples of stunning invites have each been so perfect for the weddings we have attended. Each has said so much about the wedding style and the couple.<br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1078/4732592340_4a725bbc77_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1078/4732592340_4a725bbc77_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1370/4732592680_8eaed50887_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1370/4732592680_8eaed50887_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1194/4732592834_8b7ba96d87_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1194/4732592834_8b7ba96d87_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br>Stationary designed by <a href="http://www.etsy.com/shop/EnfinLaVoila">Marijke </a><br><br>We have so many people to thank for support over the past few months. It would take a lot of time to name you all, but we want to send a huge Thank You to our parents and families for their love and support since we have gone full time and also our dear friends across the UK (Oxford, Suffolk, Birmingham, Pembrokeshire...)<br>A huge Thank You has to go out to all the wonderful couples we have had the pleasure to take photos of. We love doing your weddings and we are truly honoured that you choose us. Thank You from the bottom of our hearts x o&c <br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1174/4732592946_391e59a2c8_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1174/4732592946_391e59a2c8_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1194/4732593060_8480e61d01_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1194/4732593060_8480e61d01_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1002/4731949335_25cfce56c4_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1002/4731949335_25cfce56c4_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br>Stationary designed by bride and groom.<br><br>When choosing invites and wedding stationary, dont copy these because you like them, choose something that is YOU. Something that will be part of your wedding day and will set you apart from the rest. There are some great designers out there. Try <a href="http://www.etsy.com/">Etsy</a> and <a href="http://www.folksy.com/">Folksy</a> for a range of designs that are quirky and made with love.<br>Happy stationary hunting and Thank You for taking time to read and follow our blog<br>x o&c<br><br>Please contact us if you are interested in our work here at <a href="http://www.oacphotography.com/wedding.html">www.oacphotography.com </a>', 'Two little words x', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'two-little-words-x', '', '', '2010-06-25 07:16:00', '2010-06-25 07:16:00', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.84/oc/?p=213', 0, 'post', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (298, 1, '2010-06-23 17:40:00', '2010-06-23 17:40:00', 'Our final model of the shoot was the very lovely Natalieh. She wore the most stunning vintage dress with silk gloves. Her outfit fitted perfectly with the atmosphere on the Harmony II Yacht (where the g2g had been based), so we opted for taking some shots on the stunning boat. The views from the boat provided us with a great background too. On one side were modern buildings, where the other side provided us with colourful housing and docked boats which helped to capture the feeling of being at sea (well, imagine!) Thank you Natalieh for modelling for us, it was much appreciated, especially at the end of a long hot day. Also a big and final thank you to all those lovely people who gave their time and skills to help making the day so truly-wonderful!<br><br>Venue The Harmony II <a href="http://www.harmonyyachtclub.com/">www.harmonyyachtclub.com/</a><br>Dresses <a href="http://www.vintagedress.co.uk/">www.vintagedress.co.uk</a>/<br>China and table styling <a href="http://vintageteasets.co.uk/">www.vintageteasets.co.uk</a><br>Catering was from McBaile <a href="http://www.mcbaile.com/">www.mcbaile.com</a>/<br>Cakes: Sheona''s of Cake Matters <a href="http://www.cakematters.co.uk/index.html">www.cakematters.co.uk/</a> <br>Flowers: Floriture <a href="http://www.floriture.com/">www.floriture.com</a><br>Lilly MUA <a href="http://www.modelmayhem.com/">www.modelmayhem.com/1075740</a><br>Heather Talbot <a href="http://www.modelmayhem.com/">www.modelmayhem.com/1192627</a><br>Cat Parnell (also did hair) <a href="http://www.catparnell.tk/">www.catparnell.tk/</a><br>Sara Friar <a href="http://www.heygorgeous.me.uk/bodypainting.html">www.heygorgeous.me.uk/bodypainting.html</a><br>Silvi <a href="http://www.modelmayhem.com/">www.modelmayhem.com/portfolio/1216312/0</a><br>Clara B <a href="http://www.modelmayhem.com/">www.modelmayhem.com/1417038</a><br>Nat <a href="http://www.modelmayhem.com/">www.modelmayhem.com/1363531</a><br>Miss Cherry Delight (Gemma) <a href="http://www.modelmayhem.com/">www.modelmayhem.com/1663173</a><br>Siobhan <a href="http://www.modelmayhem.com/">www.modelmayhem.com/1519392</a><br>Sara Friar <a href="http://www.heygorgeous.me.uk/bodypainting.html">www.heygorgeous.me.uk/bodypainting.html</a><br>Janka <a href="http://www.modelmayhem.com/">www.modelmayhem.com/1556691</a><br><br>and of course the wonderful <a href="ttp://www.thephotographyparlour.com">Photography Parlour</a> and amazing <a href="http://www.rosieparsons.com/">Rosie Parsons</a>!<br><br>Hope you have enjoyed our journey with the g2g. If you wish to see any more of our work, please dont hesitate to contact us at www.oacphotography.com x o&c <br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1131/4727075147_3a575406e2_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1131/4727075147_3a575406e2_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1201/4727733598_58310bc649_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1201/4727733598_58310bc649_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1224/4727079161_a17239938f_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1224/4727079161_a17239938f_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1400/4727079415_c58c1c94c4_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1400/4727079415_c58c1c94c4_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1151/4727079911_99809a9938_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1151/4727079911_99809a9938_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1040/4727724496_f7008dcded_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1040/4727724496_f7008dcded_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1113/4727088787_9f73bab4b3_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1113/4727088787_9f73bab4b3_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1326/4727074855_bb83657bc7_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1326/4727074855_bb83657bc7_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1381/4727088423_e1b2e2004a_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1381/4727088423_e1b2e2004a_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1228/4727720150_6c50f9cdb8_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1228/4727720150_6c50f9cdb8_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a>', 'Natalieh and Harmony (The Photography Parlour g2g)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'natalieh-and-harmony-the-photography-parlour-g2g', '', '', '2010-06-23 17:40:00', '2010-06-23 17:40:00', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.84/oc/?p=214', 0, 'post', '', 3);
INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (215, 1, '2010-06-23 17:18:00', '2010-06-23 17:18:00', 'Our second model of the day was the very lovely Clara B. As soon as we saw the stunning dress and bow she has in her hair and her lovely smile we couldnt help but hope we would have the chance to work with her. Yet again, Clara was very laid back and very easy to work with. She made our job very easy and was a very popular model amongst the photographers. We took Clara on rather a long walk around the edge of the docks for these images. The writing on the side of the docks was so striking and it made such a great background against the mono-chrome outfit and flowers that Clara was wearing. Thank you Clara for making our shoot such fun and for being so happy to do as the group asked, even climbing up on the crane (hope it didn''t scare you too much! x)<br><br>Here are links to all those wonderful people who helped in making Clara and the other models look so stunning x<br>Lilly MUA <a href="http://www.modelmayhem.com/">www.modelmayhem.com/1075740</a><br>Heather Talbot <a href="http://www.modelmayhem.com/">www.modelmayhem.com/1192627</a><br>Cat Parnell (also did hair) <a href="http://www.catparnell.tk/">www.catparnell.tk/</a><br>Sara Friar <a href="http://www.heygorgeous.me.uk/bodypainting.html">www.heygorgeous.me.uk/bodypainting.htm</a><br>Model - Clara B <a href="http://www.modelmayhem.com/1417038">www.modelmayhem.com/1417038<br></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1352/4727724724_f44248a905_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1352/4727724724_f44248a905_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1110/4727725022_019db2463f_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1110/4727725022_019db2463f_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1190/4727723258_009db1d745_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1190/4727723258_009db1d745_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href=