INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (312, 1, '2010-11-25 18:03:00', '2010-11-25 18:03:00', 'I think this blog title says it all. These guys are "truly scrumptious!". This is our final blog from the fantastic photo swap we were involved in in Bristol and what a great time we had with Shella and Derek. Shella is a truly talented photographer herself, running her own business <a href="http://www.shelldemar.com/">Shell de Mar Photography</a>. We swoon over her work regularly. With true style, flair and obvious deep love for each other, these two made taking photos easy and truly pleasurable work. I secretly had real pangs of jealousy for Shella''s fur hat! Oh, take a look at Shells <a href="http://www.shelldemar.com/blog/">blog</a> for her photos of us too! <br>We really hope you have enjoyed our images from the photo swap. It really was such a great time and although incredibly cold it was so enjoyable. Thanks to the lovely Rosie Parsons for organising the get-together and to the truly talented photographers (<a href="http://www.sugarandspicephotography.co.uk/">Juliet McKee</a>, <a href="http://www.dominiquebaderblog.com/">Dominique Bader</a>, <a href="http://www.antoninaphotography.co.uk/">Antonina Mamzeko</a>, <a href="http://www.rosieparsons.com/">Rosie Parsons</a>) that came along to play and helped to make it such fun!<br>We would be more than happy and interested in doing Photoswaps in the future if anyone fancies it. Drop us a line, lets make plans! <br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5045/5207251642_83401a8794.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5045/5207251642_83401a8794.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4089/5207251472_70af4972d8.jpg"><img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4089/5207251472_70af4972d8.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5201/5207251080_ac0ab71594.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5201/5207251080_ac0ab71594.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5285/5206654221_9b2b63e99f.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5285/5206654221_9b2b63e99f.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5288/5207252072_90b430b2d2.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5288/5207252072_90b430b2d2.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4106/5207252298_9700da0999.jpg"><img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4106/5207252298_9700da0999.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5090/5206654903_301afc59f6.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5090/5206654903_301afc59f6.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5121/5206655103_cf6c997ff4.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5121/5206655103_cf6c997ff4.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5202/5206655301_6f24b621b9.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5202/5206655301_6f24b621b9.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5003/5206655495_00fa845183.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5003/5206655495_00fa845183.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4125/5206655653_d8488cff8f.jpg"><img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4125/5206655653_d8488cff8f.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5090/5207253452_a4c92a2aa8.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5090/5207253452_a4c92a2aa8.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4126/5206656027_df8f743c55.jpg"><img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4126/5206656027_df8f743c55.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br>If you like what you see you can see more here at <a href="http://www.oacphotography.com/wedding.html">www.oacphotography.com</a>', 'Truly Scrumptious! - PhotoSwap - Post#4 {Charis}', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'truly-scrumptious-p