INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (321, 1, '2011-05-23 08:50:00', '2011-05-23 08:50:00', 'This weekend we didnt have a wedding to shoot, so we invited some friends over to play. We didnt quite know how the weather would treat us. We luckily had a let up in the rain, so while Owen and Tim rocked it out on guitars, having a jam and music practice, I took these three lovely ladies outside for some fun! Pilar was also shooting with me as she was trying to decide whether she liked a 24-70mm lens we had for sale. By the end of the shoot, lets just say, it is no longer ours! (success!)<br>Sofi and Feli are two of the cutest most lovely sisters. They are loving and supportive, they are fun and crazy! You cant beat that!<br>Hope these photos make you chuckle, because Ive been giggling throughout preparing this blog. Hope you all have a great week, with plenty of reasons to smile and plenty of reasons to pull crazy faces, do funny dances and give big cuddles! x o&c<br><br><a href="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3610/5750275712_de10022261_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3610/5750275712_de10022261_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5189/5750276624_79c9750881_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5189/5750276624_79c9750881_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2204/5749730973_bb65a4e873_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2204/5749730973_bb65a4e873_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5023/5750277120_51b546e16d_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5023/5750277120_51b546e16d_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3541/5750277840_52663b631a_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3541/5750277840_52663b631a_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3324/5750278090_6bebea3437_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3324/5750278090_6bebea3437_b.jp