INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (324, 1, '2011-04-27 10:23:00', '2011-04-27 10:23:00', 'A wedding? A wedding this week? Seriously? <br>A party? A party with cake? Seriously? why not!<br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5184/5660602047_73a74b69c4_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5184/5660602047_73a74b69c4_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br>With all the excitement of the Royal Wedding we thought it only right to join in the fun too, so we invited two of our very special friends to our house for a little bit of a Royal Wedding tea party. Cakes, bunting, union jacks, moustaches, banners and even some fancy hats!<br>We dont really think this needs much explaining... where there are little people, there is fun - FACT! Where there are cakes and decorations, there is a party - FACT! Where there are photographers, there are photos- FACT!<br>Hope you enjoy seeing what we got up to. Make sure you also make your way down to the bottom of this blog for a truly lovely video of some more shenanigans!<br>What ever and however you choose to join in the celebrations of the Royal Wedding, we hope you have loads of fun! Congrats Will and Kate! - Marriage is pretty fabulous! x o&c<br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5148/5660374899_b5dc09405f_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5148/5660374899_b5dc09405f_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5021/5660375037_d51aae5755_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5021/5660375037_d51aae5755_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5068/5660375141_84e61480d8_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5068/5660375141_84e61480d8_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5308/5660944216_3a98d37f57_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5308/5660944216_3a98d37f57_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5223/5660944442_c47b8ae2d8