INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (329, 1, '2011-03-14 11:29:00', '2011-03-14 11:29:00', 'You always hope and pray that a wedding in winter will be dry, will be light and warm enough!. Our first 2011 wedding was all of these. Rachel and Lee got married in Milford Haven, Pembrokeshire and had their reception at the <a href="http://www.wolfscastle.com/restaurant">Allt-yr-Afon</a> on January 29th. It was as local as it possibly can be for us, literally five minutes from our house. Perfect!  <br>Rachel wore a dress by <a href="http://www.miamiabridal.co.uk/">MiaMia</a>, with a stunning lace shrug by <a href="http://www.sassiholford.com/">Sassi Holford</a>. Her feathers were <a href="http://www.sassobridalaccessories.net/">Sasso</a>, with shoes by <a href="http://rachelsimpsonshoes.co.uk/">Rachel Simpson</a> and headdress by <a href="http://www.jennypackham.com/">Jenny Packham</a>. A truly designer outfit - All thanks to the lovely Sally and Ali at "<a href="http://www.whitebride.net/">White Bride</a>" in Narbeth (a truly stunning boutique with some of the most beautiful designer dresses and wedding accessories. We are looking forward hugely to capturing more "White Bride" brides this year!)<br>It was such a stunning outfit to photograph. The feathers added such a great texture and really suited Rachel (to be honest, Ive not seen many brides who carry this look off so well!) Lee too looked very dapper in his top hat and tails and fabulous cane, as did his ushers. <br>Rachel and Lee have the most wonderful little family. Ffion, their daughter is the cutest little lady and she truly stole the show for us! We love the photos of Ffion with her parents. You can really feel the joy, love and pleasure they have from being a family. Congratulations to Rachel and Lee, whose family will be ever increasing sometime in the next few months! :D <br>Anyway, rather than rattling on, have a look and please leave us a comment. We love to know what you think and we know how much brides and grooms love feeling the love too!<br>Thanks so much for letting us be part of your day! x x o&c<br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5132/5526038702_0d64342411_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5132/5526038702_0d64342411_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5020/5526038806_9edf8e5e85_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5020/5526038806_9edf8e5e85_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5092/5526038926_87fd402c41_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5092/5526038926_87fd402c41_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5137/5526039538_a31162e00f_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5137/5526039538_a31162e00f_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5298/5525444945_f4d7f7394c_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5298/5525444945_f4d7f7394c_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5291/5526039006_e7754bed5e_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5291/5526039006_e7754bed5e_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5140/5526039722_2b4a942697_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5140/5526039722_2b4a942697_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5254/5526039786_387543290d_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5254/5526039786_387543290d_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5092/5525445213_ee7bb8c944_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5092/5525445213_ee7bb8c944_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5254/5526039958_04b200488e_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5254/5526039958_04b200488e_o.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><br><a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5219/5525445403_c6516af69f_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm6.static.flic