INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (339, 1, '2012-02-20 14:00:00', '2012-02-20 14:00:00', 'When we spoke to David and Natasha about their wedding plans we knew their would lots of glamour and style. Both David and Natasha are from Blackpool, but chose to come over the border to celebrate their wedding in North Wales. They had both their ceremony and reception in the grand grounds of <a href="http://www.soughtonhall.co.uk/">Soughton Hall.</a><br>With their wedding theme based around Chanel, there was detail in abundance. From details decorating the main house, to the grounds and the marquee where their reception was held. The main decoration was styled and created by the uber-talented and very lovely <a href="http://avaeventstyling.co.uk/">"Ava Events Styling"</a> they worked endlessly to make the wedding situation look truly top class. With table names based on Chanel perfumes, beautifully cut glass perfume bottles and pearls, roses and ribbon adorning every aspect of the day, we felt quite spoilt by how much detail there was for our photographing pleasure!<br>Natasha is such a petit person, but carried off her dress and <a href="http://www.dior.com/couture/en_gb">Christian Dior</a> shoes with real professionalism... like its something she would wear everyday! (I know I couldn''t walk in heals that high!)<br>Hope you enjoy gazing at some of the style and design carried through this wedding day. Thank you for choosing us to capture your wedding day David and Natasha and also congratulations on becoming an Uncle and Aunty this week! Very exciting stuff! x o&c<br><br><a href="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7024/6795376579_025263c922_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7024/6795376579_025263c922_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7171/6795361985_fa5563b767_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7171/6795361985_fa5563b767_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7149/6795362583_504c028