INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (347, 1, '2011-10-20 12:16:00', '2011-10-20 12:16:00', 'Firstly, we feel we need to apologise for a serious lack of blog posts this summer. With weddings from May to September we''ve been so busy. Now we are on a little October break before weddings in the last 2 months of 2012 and have some real treats for you, so please dont stay away too long, you might miss something!<br><br>Right, anyway back to it... Gavin and Shelley got married! yes they did!<br>It was a super hot day, super sunny and generally super all round. Neither Gavin or Shelley wanted getting ready shots, so we met them at the church. They got married in the tiny Carmarthenshire village and then we scooped them away for their couple shots at <a href="http://www.llanegwad-carmarthen.co.uk/atttractpaxton.htm">Paxtons Tower</a>. Its one of our favourite spots and the history behind it is quite interesting. We love it. Its got a certain "Shrek" appeal and the views are quite stunning. Gavin and Shelley are both quite shy when it comes to the camera, but we think they did a grand job of being themselves and we loved the time we spent up on the hill with the cows and powerful sunshine. It was beautiful.<br>They held their reception at <a href="http://www.thefigtreerestaurant.co.uk/">The Fig Tree</a>. Shelley runs her own <a href="http://www.thevintageteapartyco.com/">vintage crockery hire business and shop</a>, so the wedding carried a vintage theme that ran through from her dress to the beautiful dcor at the reception. It was so delicately and thoughtfully put together. We highly recommend Shelleys business <a href="http://www.thevintageteapartyco.com/">"The Vintage Tea Party Company"</a> for all your crockery hire needs.<br>The Fig Tree provided both the main wedding breakfast and evening hog roast and boy, did it taste good!<br>With dancing and celebrating late into the evening we loved being part of this special wedding celebration and want to thank Gavin and Shelley again for choosing us as their wedding photographers x <br><br><a href="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6168/6263005789_498a4dbf85_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6168/6263005789_498a4dbf85_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6115/6263011059_2a52f02a33_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6115/6263011059_2a52f02a33_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6174/6263008799_3f51f11174_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6174/6263008799_3f51f11174_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6118/6263533662_c02858cb23_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6118/6263533662_c02858cb23_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6034/6263527468_372433a33c_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6034/6263527468_372433a33c_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6214/6263005173_197e730fed_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6214/6263005173_197e730fed_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6046/6263003865_351b41256e_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6046/6263003865_351b41256e_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6175/6263006597_c2e589a0d4_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6175/6263006597_c2e589a0d4_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6049/6263535144_4b64c14620_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6049/6263535144_4b64c14620_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6240/6263006079_3276b21b2b_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6240/6263006079_3276b21b2b_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6050/6263002997_408b31c20e_b.jpg"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6050/6263002997_408b31c20e_b.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="ht