INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (354, 1, '2013-04-29 11:04:00', '2013-04-29 11:04:00', '<div>Genuinely lovely people. Gareth and Lucinda are genuinely lovely people.</div>\n<div>We thoroughly enjoyed every second photographing the wedding of Gareth and Lucinda last year. They are so genuine, so real, so vivacious and just the sort of people that make you feel really at ease.</div>\n<div>Their wedding was an accumulation of love for each other, love for their own personal life adventures and for their friends and family. There was so much laughter and fun, that even an incident with the wedding car breaking down and smoke pouring out of the dashboard didn''t put a dampener of any of it. In fact, its these things that add to the memories. </div>\n<div>Both have travelled and have made memories in many different parts of the world. Their wedding represented that. With readings in Spanish, paper bunting from South America and their reception at the very beautiful <a href="http://www.bartholomewbarn.co.uk/">Bartholomew Barn</a> in West Sussex. A combination that worked perfectly and was so visually appealing. Adorned with lavender and rosemary sprigs, there was such a beautiful smell in the air all day too.</div>\n<div>Looking back at these photos, I love the vibrancy of the grass and the feeling of warmth and sunshine. (Longing for a bit more of that this spring/summer, purrrlease!!!)</div>\n<div>G and Lu, thank you so much for choosing us to capture and share in your day. You guys are so awesome and we loved every second of your day. We hope you love looking back at your day as much as we have x o&c </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-AIkoPvJ9W_I/UX5Kf9ubjfI/AAAAAAAADto/FEwL0dd1cwc/s1600/Gareth+and+Lucinda-0006.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-AIkoPvJ9W_I/UX5Kf9ubjfI/AAAAAAAADto/FEwL0dd1cwc/s1600/Gareth+and+Lucinda-0006.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-6s9dxkL6FjE/UX5Kgm2xpvI/AA