INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (130, 1, '2013-02-27 12:39:00', '2013-02-27 12:39:00', '<div>Oh my goodness, Ive really loved looking through these photos again. What a complete pleasure!</div>\n<div>Yep, we are still blogging weddings from last year and yes, we have some truly beautiful, fun, special weddings still in pipeline. This wedding is certainly no exception!</div>\n<div>We have already had this wedding featured on the wonderful <a href="http://www.rockmywedding.co.uk/we-were-always-meant-to-be/">Rock My Wedding </a>blog, with a feature about this wedding and a full fabulous description about the day from the lovely Clare. Please take a look at the feature, its pretty ace!</div>\n<div>In a nutshell. The wonderful Tom and Clare were married in a truly beautiful, personal and precious ceremony in a small and local church to where Clare and her family are originally from. They then held their wedding reception back at Colin''s Field. With tipis, welly wanging, coconut shy, home-made cakes, handmade cheese, game pie, hay bales, dressing up tent and plenty of gorgeous friends and family, there was without a doubt, no chance that there wouldn''t be a hell of a lot of fun had at this special wedding celebration.</div>\n<div>We had such a great time being able to explore the beautiful woods and barn too and from start to finish really appreciated the freedom Tom and Clare gave both of us to capture their day in our style, with opportunity to be relaxed and creative. We love this so much and appreciate it hugely. Basically, Tom and Clare we love you! You are fun, brilliant, exciting, perfect for each other and some of the kindest, most thoughtful people we have ever worked with. Thank you for a truly fabulous day. Still smiling and laughing when we think back to your wedding day and your engagement shoot (which we must blog, slightly out of order but we must blog!)</div>\n<div>Happy happy relaxed and tipi festival vibes all the way today x o&c</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3eSRFULNs-A/US3yE6HVi8I/AAAAAAAACeE/G43feq4Guic/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0003.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3eSRFULNs-A/US3yE6HVi8I/AAAAAAAACeE/G43feq4Guic/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0003.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4JxxZOHq33o/US3yG7xrr1I/AAAAAAAACeM/ML2z2Vtn6tQ/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0005.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4JxxZOHq33o/US3yG7xrr1I/AAAAAAAACeM/ML2z2Vtn6tQ/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0005.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-5x3wdZ_tKcQ/US3yHCrwBRI/AAAAAAAACeQ/FK5d5E17ZqM/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0004.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-5x3wdZ_tKcQ/US3yHCrwBRI/AAAAAAAACeQ/FK5d5E17ZqM/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0004.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-a3tIJb-lhaE/US3yHe9nu0I/AAAAAAAACeU/_LRGNnEFml4/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0009.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-a3tIJb-lhaE/US3yHe9nu0I/AAAAAAAACeU/_LRGNnEFml4/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0009.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-etdPisA0kPY/US3yI5p6WzI/AAAAAAAACek/59TOBo5JOdc/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0010.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-etdPisA0kPY/US3yI5p6WzI/AAAAAAAACek/59TOBo5JOdc/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0010.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-HiC6oLGHxI4/US3yK2xpShI/AAAAAAAACes/SwGMpzoVBWo/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0013.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-HiC6oLGHxI4/US3yK2xpShI/AAAAAAAACes/SwGMpzoVBWo/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0013.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Vht-5fKJxek/US3yLaYydpI/AAAAAAAACe0/CZDVMze0000/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0015.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Vht-5fKJxek/US3yLaYydpI/AAAAAAAACe0/CZDVMze0000/s1600/Tom+and+Clare-0015.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZaOU5BJ8Lws/US3yM4EcrXI/AAAAAAAACe8/L-uw1WhaFvw/s1600/Tom