INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (132, 1, '2013-01-15 09:00:00', '2013-01-15 09:00:00', '<div>Euan and Beth. From the moment we first met them we knew these guys would make our cameras smile. Indeed they did.</div>\n<div>We initially met Euan and Beth at a very lovely pub in London, 5 months before their big day, after they saw on of our weddings on the awesome <a href="http://www.rockmywedding.co.uk/we-were-always-meant-to-be/">Rock My Wedding blog</a>. We loved Euans duffel coat and Beths beautiful eyes. They made us smile and excited about shooting their wedding day. </div>\n<div>When their day finally came around it was like catching up with friends we had not seen for a few months.</div>\n<div>Beths dress was such a beautiful, personal and original statement. She had her mothers wedding dress re-modelled to fit and suit her. It was truly beautiful. It fitted her perfectly and she carried it off so gracefully, so effortlessly.</div>\n<div>Euan, the handsome Scot looked truly dashing in his kilt, as did his groomsmen and many other members of the McCauley family. It was a perfect fusion of Scottish and Welsh. Another cultural combination! We like them... a lot!</div>\n<div>Euan and Beth were married in Beths home town of Brecon, with their ceremony at the <a href="http://www.breconcastle.co.uk/">Castle Hotel </a>and then their reception held in a marquee in the local rugby club. The dcor and the styling in the marquee was so relaxed, yet so pretty it really didn''t feel like it was on the pitch where many a sweaty Welsh rugby player has been tackled. With <a href="http://www.thisbus.com/">London Route-master </a>bus, <a href="http://www.shepherdsicecream.co.uk/shows_events.htm">Shepard''s ice cream </a>van ( with ice cream made from sheep milk!) and a fair serving of hilarious speeches, the whole wedding day was as inidividal and perfect as Euan and Beth. We hope these photos speak for themselves. Beauty, graceful, real and full of a real deep love and friendship that was such an honour to witness.</div>\n<div>Thank you lovely people for choosing us to share in and capture your day. Big love x o&c </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-uXDS481HQy4/UO7XiFV7nLI/AAAAAAAACNM/dXytrazpDwc/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0001.jpg"><img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-uXDS481HQy4/UO7XiFV7nLI/AAAAAAAACNM/dXytrazpDwc/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0001.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--_XhtGs0TGA/UO7Xm1sHUhI/AAAAAAAACNs/_xZfmboViNc/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0025.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--_XhtGs0TGA/UO7Xm1sHUhI/AAAAAAAACNs/_xZfmboViNc/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0025.jpg"></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AZvlCN6bfhA/UO7XjHzyRwI/AAAAAAAACNU/o1Hjog3FBxE/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0023.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AZvlCN6bfhA/UO7XjHzyRwI/AAAAAAAACNU/o1Hjog3FBxE/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0023.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-VA-zyhy6yxE/UO7XlSfKqlI/AAAAAAAACNk/eQz6kGWrt_M/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0024.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-VA-zyhy6yxE/UO7XlSfKqlI/AAAAAAAACNk/eQz6kGWrt_M/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0024.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qk0C0Dn08NU/UO7Xn1bBjhI/AAAAAAAACN4/pipiVbOW-hE/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0026.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qk0C0Dn08NU/UO7Xn1bBjhI/AAAAAAAACN4/pipiVbOW-hE/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0026.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-xMmLQ5Rriss/UO7XsaPJ5uI/AAAAAAAACOI/dYqTNbHYoKI/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0031.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-xMmLQ5Rriss/UO7XsaPJ5uI/AAAAAAAACOI/dYqTNbHYoKI/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0031.jpg"></a></div>\n<div>\n<a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-_FDvMUyPsKY/UO7XsmgzAjI/AAAAAAAACOE/t3hbfZdNVmA/s1600/Euan+and+Beth-0043.jpg"><img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-IOFGoATekqQ/UO7Xt7EFuQI/AAAAAAAACOQ/X5luhmgM