INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (365, 1, '2013-06-12 14:07:00', '2013-06-12 14:07:00', '<div>Kieron and Hannah, two Bristolites, decided to spend their wedding day in the city that they love. They held their wedding ceremony and party at <a href="http://www.bristolzoo.org.uk/">Bristol Zoo</a>, choosing to have their wedding photos in and around the areas of Bristol that are special to them.</div>\n<div>Hannah, in her purple dress and Kieron in his grey suit, were the perfect picture of love, friendship and romance all day. It was so great to share in their big day and see the joy and happiness that they bring to each other.</div>\n<div>Although their day was held in the grounds of the zoo, both Kieron and Hannah are not big animal fans, choosing the venue for a place for their family and friends to enjoy and because of the wedding reception venue itself, rather than a chance to see penguin and big cats.</div>\n<div>Venturing from their venue was by far the best choice we made, the sun shone and it was so obvious that these guys love and feel totally at home in Bristol. A stop off at the suspension bridge was a must, then to the truly gorgeous doors of "The Rocks Garage". We then took a trip to the street where they live (very Pigmalian) before heading on back for a good old celebration and slap up meal.</div>\n<div>Kieron and Hannah, we loved sharing in your day and having the pleasure of caputring photos that we know have made you smile.</div>\n<div>Thank you again for such a lovely day. We hope you look back with much joy and happiness x o&c</div>\n<div>p.s: we told you you were photogenic! :P x x </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-orfdSCn3cL8/UbhYyxGx4RI/AAAAAAAAEvk/_reuSEBc1ZU/s1600/Kieron+and+Hannah-0003.jpg"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-orfdSCn3cL8/UbhYyxGx4RI/AAAAAAAAEvk/_reuSEBc1ZU/s1600/Kieron+and+Hannah-0003.jpg"></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0FHkTlocTEA/UbhYx8jKKyI/AAAAAAAAEvY/_kFWn