INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (370, 1, '2013-07-15 14:43:04', '2013-07-15 14:43:04', '<div></div>\nNick and Emma are such an awesome team. I feel it would be more appropriate to actually call them "Team Nick&amp; Emma". They work perfectly together, supporiting each other, loving each other, understanding each other and working through whatever life brings their way.\nWe had the true honour of capturing their wedding day last summer in the beautiful welsh city of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/St_Davids">St Davids.</a> I call it a city, as it has a stunning cathedral. Its actually Britain''s smallest city, both in size and population. Its a beautiful little place and worth a visit.\nIts cathedral is something quite spectacular and made the most stunning back drop for the ceremony.\nNick and Emma are both super-duper fit, outdoorsey people and it was totally fitting therefore to take time out after their big day to head on down to Whitesands beach for some couple shots, before heading on back up to enjoy their party. (We actually shot their pre shoot on Whitesands too, a few days before their big day, but we will be sharing some of this soon in a separate post)\nBack at the reception there was such a buzz of joy and excitement from all their guests, family and friends, well and truly an honour to be a part of and to share in some of the love that so many people feel for Nick and Emma. As you will see, these guys know how to party hard too and their awesome band "The Zen Hussies" made it impossible not to groove. Thank you so much for choosing us to share in and capture your wonderful wedding day "Team Nick and Emma!" :Looking forward to hanging out again soon P x o&amp;c\n\nSince their big day, Nick and Emma have set up their awesome business called "<a href="http://www.thecoffeecamper.com/">The Coffee Camper</a>".\nBasically a cute and very cool 1976 Citroen van converted to sell ethically sourced coffee, cakes and other yummy products. We would highly recommend these guys to anyone fancying something a little big different at their wedding celebration. Ive heard they make the most scrummy flapjack!\n<div></div>\n<div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-7jzh0LkOmhU/UYJMiGTbpaI/AAAAAAAAD2g/1U6sbcIVV3M/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0002.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-7jzh0LkOmhU/UYJMiGTbpaI/AAAAAAAAD2g/1U6sbcIVV3M/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0002.jpg" border="0" /></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-kmJx6sgTfZY/UYJMlItAAQI/AAAAAAAAD24/e_Bs25-Lh34/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0008.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-kmJx6sgTfZY/UYJMlItAAQI/AAAAAAAAD24/e_Bs25-Lh34/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0008.jpg" border="0" /></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-H56PzfbUVcM/UYJMpTRvkmI/AAAAAAAAD3Q/2vdF5SxQlb8/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0012.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-H56PzfbUVcM/UYJMpTRvkmI/AAAAAAAAD3Q/2vdF5SxQlb8/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0012.jpg" border="0" /></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ChTDdxrO0w8/UYJMl2-2vsI/AAAAAAAAD3A/c_MNc4Pco2U/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0015.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ChTDdxrO0w8/UYJMl2-2vsI/AAAAAAAAD3A/c_MNc4Pco2U/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0015.jpg" border="0" /></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/--DlZ5Pvsffs/UYJMpwVKabI/AAAAAAAAD3Y/yziv0yTVkps/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0016.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/--DlZ5Pvsffs/UYJMpwVKabI/AAAAAAAAD3Y/yziv0yTVkps/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0016.jpg" border="0" /></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-XIkwLeeoE60/UYJMo76fUeI/AAAAAAAAD3I/EspNGzVn8fY/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0019.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-XIkwLeeoE60/UYJMo76fUeI/AAAAAAAAD3I/EspNGzVn8fY/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0019.jpg" border="0" /></a></div>\n<div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-7kqo8nAwj1A/UYJMq1xjZ5I/AAAAAAAAD3g/xGtySf8U-is/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0022.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-7kqo8nAwj1A/UYJMq1xjZ5I/AAAAAAAAD3g/xGtySf8U-is/s1600/Nick+and+Emma-0022.jpg" border="0" />