INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (634, 1, '2013-09-12 12:08:00', '2013-09-12 12:08:00', '<div dir="ltr" trbidi="on"><div>We just love hearing how our couples met and the journey they take to get to their wedding celebration. Martin and Victoria met at<a href="http://www.llandaffrc.com/"> Llandaff Rowing Club</a> in Cardiff where they were both in different rowing squads. Fast forward a few years and one very hot and sunny day in June this lovely pair said "I do" and celebrated with their family and friends at the very rowing club where their friendship first blossomed.</div><div>In a truly beautiful <a href="http://www.jennypackham.com/">Jenny Packham</a> dress Victoria met her man at the alter. Martin looked pretty daper in his <a href="http://www.viviennewestwood.co.uk/">Vivienne Westwood</a> tie and sharp navy suit. Exchanging amazing <a href="http://www.tiffany.co.uk/">Tiffany</a> rings, its fair to say these guys are great taste.</div><div>Back at the rowing club, the sun shone, there was icecream treats, a cake competition, lego table settings, flowers in trophy tankards and a beautiful "memory tree" with photos of precious people.</div><div>Fair to say it was a very personal, very special wedding day. Thank you so much Martin and Victoria for choosing us to capture your wedding celebration. Still look at the cakes from your competition and drool x o&c</div><div><br></div><div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-i5WYXlye4o8/UjGkjzLNbwI/AAAAAAAAF7U/6fPaXNMve9Y/s1600/Martin+and+Victoria-0004.jpg"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-i5WYXlye4o8/UjGkjzLNbwI/AAAAAAAAF7U/6fPaXNMve9Y/s1600/Martin+and+Victoria-0004.jpg"></a></div><div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-NdW68bTVq9Q/UjGkj_UWKKI/AAAAAAAAF7Y/20g7Bl_f96k/s1600/Martin+and+Victoria-0006.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-NdW68bTVq9Q/UjGkj_UWKKI/AAAAAAAAF7Y/20g7Bl_f96k/s1600/Martin+and+Victoria-0006.jpg"></a></div><div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-OvaFi0CrdS