INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (635, 1, '2013-08-29 10:36:00', '2013-08-29 10:36:00', '<div dir="ltr" trbidi="on">We met Neil and Gemma at the <a href="http://www.pembrokeshireweddingfayre.com/">Pembrokeshire Wedding Fair</a> and I remember Neil looking through our work. They then went away. Neil then came back and had another look and went away.<br>I remember thinking, "Oooo, maybe he likes what we do?"<br>Time passed and we had an email enquiring a little more. "Oooo, I think he does like what we do!"<br>Jump forward about 9 months, a couple of meet ups and a pint or two, chats about cricket and this day happened!<br>We love Neil and Gemma and really feel like we can call them friends. They are honest, open, real and brimming with warmth and love for each other and those near and dear to them.<br>To see the happiness shining from their faces on their big day was pretty overwhelming. A real contentment and security in knowing where they belong.<br>They were married in a small church, the same church that Gemmas parents and Grandparents had married in and held their reception at the beautiful <a href="http://www.pictoncastle.co.uk/">Picton Castle.</a><br>The weather was divine. With drinks and canapes in the walled garden, they headed on back to a marquee. Decorated with flowers and a large "memory tree", on which hung wedding photos of many of Neil and Gemmas family and friends. This is was an absolutely perfect tribute to love, loved ones and to the beauty of marriage.<br>The food at this wedding was, without a doubt, hands down, the most amazing food we have ever had at a wedding. <a href="http://holdenscatering.com/">Holden Catering</a> you are culinary magicians! We will be recommending you to the world!<br>Once all the amazing food was consumed and the brilliantly fun and personal speeches were completed (Neil and entourage sighed with relief!) this wonderful pair danced the night away to "<a href="http://www.irockband.co.uk/">iRock</a>" (another highly recommended wedding service).<br>We also had the privilege of working alongside the equally lovely and talented <a href="http://www.benwaltonfilms.co.uk/">Ben Walton Films</a> for the first time. Enjoy taking a peek at this handy work too at the end of this post. Its pretty! <br><br>Neil and Gemma, you guys have made us smile so much. We have loved the journey we have travelled with you to create your wedding photos and we appreciate the truly beautiful emails you have sent us. There have been tears of happiness, believe me! Hope we see you soon x x x o&c<br><br><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--EPbL6be56o/Uh8ZNuMwWDI/AAAAAAAAFuU/c9XIRsbA8t0/s1600/Neil+and+Gemma-0004.jpg"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--EPbL6be56o/Uh8ZNuMwWDI/AAAAAAAAFuU/c9XIRsbA8t0/s1600/Neil+and+Gemma-0004.jpg"></a><br><div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-tGBSaNEv9RI/Uh8ZNj7GlzI/AAAAAAAAFuY/wbu2LDoPrPU/s1600/Neil+and+Gemma-0002.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-tGBSaNEv9RI/Uh8ZNj7GlzI/AAAAAAAAFuY/wbu2LDoPrPU/s1600/Neil+and+Gemma-0002.jpg"></a></div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-eK30uAY8VtA/Uh8ZN8gR_BI/AAAAAAAAFug/oRBfAzVn_N0/s1600/Neil+and+Gemma-0001.jpg"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-eK30uAY8VtA/Uh8ZN8gR_BI/AAAAAAAAFug/oRBfAzVn_N0/s1600/Neil+and+Gemma-0001.jpg"></a><br><div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Q3_BiMoZzFY/Uh8ZO-FXJVI/AAAAAAAAFus/q-VLQmJALo4/s1600/Neil+and+Gemma-0009.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Q3_BiMoZzFY/Uh8ZO-FXJVI/AAAAAAAAFus/q-VLQmJALo4/s1600/Neil+and+Gemma-0009.jpg"></a></div><div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PMC1h5h1Sh4/Uh8ZSmU7lcI/AAAAAAAAFvQ/hVmYeOmu6CY/s1600/Neil+and+Gemma-0011.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PMC1h5h1Sh4/Uh8ZSmU7lcI/AAAAAAAAFvQ/hVmYeOmu6CY/s1600/Neil+and+Gemma-0011.jpg"></a></div><div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-FwPogTXNGAo/Uh8ZPQpid2I/AAAAAAAAFu0/mEC7xAhD-1E/s1600/Neil+and+Gemma-0012.jpg" imag