INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (637, 1, '2013-08-13 10:27:00', '2013-08-13 10:27:00', '<div dir="ltr" trbidi="on"><div>Ric and Lizzie were fondly known to us, for a long time as "the cool jumper couple". We met them at the Pembrokeshire Wedding Fair and immediately liked their jumpers!</div><div>When we heard from them a few months later, we learnt that they were more than just "the cool jumper couple", they also like/LOVE cats, she loves Miss Marple and he isnt so keen, but loves her, so deals with it. They both have cool tattoos and are just bloomin gorgeous people! (we are big fans!)</div><div>Ric and Lizzies wedding was simple. Simple in the sense that it was a no fuss, everyone helped and every had so much fun and smiled a lot! There was a cat with a diamante collar too!</div><div>They were married on 4th July too, which made for some subtle Star Wars touches here and there. Check out Lizzies toe nail art and their Star Wars caketoppers.</div><div>With a marquee ceremony in Lizzies parents back garden, in what was a rather squeaky marquee, they tied the knot, had a tea party and danced away with family and friends. </div><div>We had the chance to scoop them away to the beautiful Little Haven for some photos and some down time. There are rather a lot of couple shots, because, quite frankly, we had the most awesome time and wanted to share with you two beautiful people on their special day.</div><div>It was such a huge honour to celebrate and share in their beautiful and fun celebration. Thank you so much "cool jumper couple" :P Much love to you and your lovely families x x o&c</div><div><br></div><div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-GUnnA4cpOgo/UgoAh4-YucI/AAAAAAAAFUo/MCtG_nuZ6bw/s1600/Rik+and+Lizzie-0004.jpg"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-GUnnA4cpOgo/UgoAh4-YucI/AAAAAAAAFUo/MCtG_nuZ6bw/s1600/Rik+and+Lizzie-0004.jpg"></a></div><div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-e-PzSlwFUKs/UgoAjceGEPI/AAAAAAAAFU8/7_c86BYo7YY/s1600/Rik+and+Lizzie-000