INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (639, 1, '2013-06-20 08:36:00', '2013-06-20 08:36:00', 'Rob and Gemma met and fell in love. Really that amazingly simple. When we first met them they had been together less than a year and were happily planning their wedding day. Love it!<br>They celebrated their wedding day at the beautiful Llangoed Hall (where we just so happen to be shooting a wedding this weekend!).<br>Their wedding day was full to the brim of memories, from their childhoods through to their time together. Two welsh dressers in the main reception room were adorned with all kinds of things from their childhood. Their first pair of shoes, first vinyls, old school books, well worn and loved teddies and beautiful photos of family members and their exciting journey.<br>Its fair to say that both Rob and Gemma were nothing but cool. Blue suede shoes for her, blue cord shoes for him. A stunning lace wedding dress for her, a blue two piece suit, with contrasting waistcoat for him.<br>With snow capped mountains in the background, but blue sky and a spring warmth to the air, the surrounding grounds made our job so enjoyable and relaxed. We loved being able to spend time with these two as the reality of what this day actually means sunk in.<br>Thank you lovely people for an awesome and fun day. We loved it. Enjoy many more adventures. Big love x o&c <br><div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SIdwKLpmNO0/UcG-A3BE7MI/AAAAAAAAE5o/E2EBlsRpgk4/s1600/Rob+and+Gemma-0003.jpg" imageanchor="1"><br></a></div><div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Weqbkk1Yul0/UcG-BQ9IaPI/AAAAAAAAE5s/Npl0iKxgWgQ/s1600/Rob+and+Gemma-0007.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Weqbkk1Yul0/UcG-BQ9IaPI/AAAAAAAAE5s/Npl0iKxgWgQ/s1600/Rob+and+Gemma-0007.jpg"></a></div><div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-kUCgfim1Z8k/UcG-EblcvJI/AAAAAAAAE6E/ShoHWnkS17I/s1600/Rob+and+Gemma-0008.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-kUCgfim1Z8k/UcG-EblcvJI/AAAAAAAA