INSERT INTO `wp_photo_posts` VALUES (666, 1, '2012-06-15 10:08:00', '2012-06-15 10:08:00', '<div>So this is the story of Theo and Lisa. Two super hot, super fun, super amazing people. They fell in love, got engaged and are now planning their amazing wedding day, which is soon to be upon us!</div><div>We had the total privilege of popping on down to beautiful Bushy Park, London for their autumnal engagement shoot.</div><div>Lisa is the queen of bargains and style and we were so chuffed and far from surprised when she appeared in her red ball gown. Theo, Mr Cool, in his leathers and trainers, again, you cant buy that style... you''re born with it! :P</div><div>I hope these photos say it all really. We had FUN!</div><div>We are so very much looking forward to their wedding day. Its going to be a bit out of the ordinary... for many different reasons.</div><div>If you''ve not seen the video (at the bottom of this blog post!) you need to watch it.... by the way, his answer was YES!</div><div>Huge thanks have to go out to lovely Kat at <a href="http://www.rocknrollbride.com/2012/01/a-rockin-a-rollin-bushy-park-engagement-shoot-theo-lisa/">Rock and Roll Bride</a> for also blogging this shoot.</div><div>Hope these photos brighten up your day, especially if the weather is anything like it is here. Autumn was the new summer I think (looking at the photos and then out of our window!)</div><div>Big love to you all, especially to you, Theo and Lisa.... so very much looking forward to celebrating with you gorgeous people! x o&c</div><div><br></div><div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-lAeASl0mNi4/T9sBJN4vC2I/AAAAAAAAAo8/BmtKeCZ0B_w/s1600/LIB+blog_067.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-lAeASl0mNi4/T9sBJN4vC2I/AAAAAAAAAo8/BmtKeCZ0B_w/s1600/LIB+blog_067.jpg"></a></div><div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-v6Ufinhac_k/T9sBGtkFb2I/AAAAAAAAAo0/iGnWa5V0CX8/s1600/LIB+blog_066.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-v6Ufinhac